<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<workout_file>
  <author>Gravel God Training</author>
  <name>W05_Sat_Apr24_NPIF_Target</name>
  <description>[MODERATE FUEL: Target 30-60g carbs/hr. Stay topped up.]

Compete - Week 5/12 - 8 weeks to Lost and Found Gravel
Phase: BASE

MAIN SET:
-2.5hr Z2 with variable power: alternate 4min @ 67% / 6min @ 78% FTP throughout
-Cadence: 82-92rpm (building efficiency)
-Position: Practice race position in final third

COOL-DOWN:
-10min easy spin Z1-Z2

PROGRESSION:
-Level 3/6: Development - Standard training load, building consistency
-Uneven segments - longer "climbs"

PURPOSE:
Terrain simulation. Variable power within Z2 for rolling course preparation.

EXECUTION:
-Focus on consistent effort and good form throughout.

NUTRITION:
-40-60g carbs/hr. Real food works well - PB&amp;J, bananas, bars.

HYDRATION:
-500-1000ml/hr depending on conditions. Include sodium.</description>
